### ============================================
### CAPM BACKEND - FULL FUNCTIONALITY TEST
### Audit Run ID: 352d30ba-d462-459d-9d38-e7f0fa256510
### ============================================

### ============================================
### PART 1: SERVICE DISCOVERY
### ============================================

### 1.1 Get Service Documents
GET http://localhost:4004/

### 1.2 Get AuditExecutionService Metadata
GET http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPAudit/$metadata

### 1.3 Get AuditReportingService Metadata
GET http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPReport/$metadata

### ============================================
### PART 2: AUDIT RUNS MANAGEMENT
### ============================================

### 2.1 Create New Audit Run (FULL Mode)
POST http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPAudit/AuditRuns
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Weekly Full Audit",
    "description": "Full audit of all permission groups and roles",
    "mode": "FULL",
    "extractGroups": true,
    "extractRoles": true,
    "sampleGroupSize": 0,
    "sampleMemberSize": 0,
    "sampleRoleSize": 0
}

### 2.2 Create New Audit Run (SAMPLE Mode - Faster)
POST http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPAudit/AuditRuns
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Sample Test Audit",
    "description": "Sample audit for testing",
    "mode": "SAMPLE",
    "extractGroups": true,
    "extractRoles": true,
    "sampleGroupSize": 5,
    "sampleMemberSize": 10,
    "sampleRoleSize": 3
}

### 2.3 Get All Audit Runs
GET http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPAudit/AuditRuns

### 2.4 Get Specific Audit Run
GET http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPAudit/AuditRuns(352d30ba-d462-459d-9d38-e7f0fa256510)

### 2.5 List Audit Runs with Filter (POST)
POST http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPAudit/listAuditRuns
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "COMPLETED",
    "top": 10,
    "skip": 0
}

### 2.6 Get Audit Status
POST http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPAudit/getAuditStatus
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "auditRunID": "352d30ba-d462-459d-9d38-e7f0fa256510"
}

### 2.7 Start Audit Manually (Use ID from 2.1)
# @prompt auditRunID
POST http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPAudit/runAudit
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "auditRunID": "{{auditRunID}}"
}

### ============================================
### PART 3: USER MANAGEMENT
### ============================================

### 3.1 Sync Users from SuccessFactors
POST http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPAudit/syncUsers
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 3.2 Get Users with Pagination
POST http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPAudit/getUsers
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "top": 20,
    "skip": 0,
    "status": "active"
}

### 3.3 Search Users by Name
POST http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPAudit/getUsers
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "search": "admin",
    "top": 10,
    "skip": 0
}

### 3.4 Get Users from Reporting Service (Entity)
GET http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPReport/Users?$top=10

### 3.5 Get Users Count
GET http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPReport/Users/$count

### ============================================
### PART 4: GROUPS
### ============================================

### 4.1 Get All Groups
GET http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPReport/Groups?$top=20

### 4.2 Get Static Groups
GET http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPReport/Groups?$filter=groupType eq 'STATIC'

### 4.3 Get Dynamic Groups
GET http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPReport/Groups?$filter=groupType eq 'DYNAMIC'

### 4.4 Get Large Groups (50+ members)
GET http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPReport/Groups?$filter=totalMemberCount gt 50

### 4.5 Get Groups Count
GET http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPReport/Groups/$count

### ============================================
### PART 5: GROUP MEMBERSHIPS
### ============================================

### 5.1 Get Group Memberships
GET http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPReport/GroupMembers?$top=50

### 5.2 Get Memberships Count
GET http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPReport/GroupMembers/$count

### 5.3 Get Members of Specific Group
# @prompt groupID
GET http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPReport/GroupMembers?$filter=groupID eq '{{groupID}}'&$top=20

### ============================================
### PART 6: ROLES
### ============================================

### 6.1 Get All Roles
GET http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPReport/Roles?$top=20

### 6.2 Get Roles Count
GET http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPReport/Roles/$count

### 6.3 Get Unused Roles
GET http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPReport/UnusedRoles?$filter=auditRunID_ID eq 352d30ba-d462-459d-9d38-e7f0fa256510

### ============================================
### PART 7: ANALYTICS - MULTI-GROUP USERS (Risk Analysis)
### ============================================

### 7.1 Get All Multi-Group Users
GET http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPReport/MultiGroupUsers?$top=50

### 7.2 Get High Risk Users
GET http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPReport/MultiGroupUsers?$filter=riskLevel eq 'High'&$top=20

### 7.3 Get Multi-Group Users Count
GET http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPReport/MultiGroupUsers/$count

