### ============================================
### QUICK TEST SEQUENCE (Run in Order)
### ============================================

### Quick Test 1: Create Audit Run
POST http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPAudit/AuditRuns
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Quick Test",
    "description": "Quick verification test",
    "mode": "SAMPLE",
    "extractGroups": true,
    "extractRoles": true,
    "sampleGroupSize": 3,
    "sampleMemberSize": 5,
    "sampleRoleSize": 2
}

### Quick Test 2: Start Audit (Use ID from above)
# @prompt auditRunID
POST http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPAudit/runAudit
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "auditRunID": "{{auditRunID}}"
}

### Quick Test 3: Check Status (Wait 10 seconds then run)
POST http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPAudit/getAuditStatus
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "auditRunID": "{{auditRunID}}"
}

### Quick Test 4: View Groups
GET http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPReport/Groups?$top=5

### Quick Test 5: View Users
GET http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPReport/Users?$top=5

### Quick Test 6: View High Risk Users
GET http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPReport/MultiGroupUsers?$filter=riskLevel eq 'High'&$top=10